show.description: A determined young woman battles betrayal, love, and family chaos while seeking justice for her imprisoned father. As her world collides with her legal aid’s ambition and deceit, buried secrets begin to surface. In a web of lies and emotions, every choice draws her closer to redemption—or ruin.
